{"tid":2131697,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"士沙證供矛盾 青年脫襲警罪","createTime":"2020-07-30T04:26:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-30T04:43:51.000Z","uid":25558,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"0b56a84df055c1c13263a0c95529f89bc84dfd65","tid":2131697,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T04:26:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200730/QLAIQW2SU725YCNBQVJTUDSNMU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200730%2FQLAIQW2SU725YCNBQVJTUDSNMU%2F&d=6fRpkjTAYTcnGOSNIV5vhG2%2BFslq3%2Bj4herl9tsBg9w%3D&h=e578abe2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200730%2FQLAIQW2SU725YCNBQVJTUDSNMU%2F&h=912322e4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200730/QLAIQW2SU725YCNBQVJTUDSNMU/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n士沙證供矛盾 青年脫襲警罪<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/mlwkpbW-WK-o5xdbxiEO32-VAfM=/1325x745/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/OMBKHNPXXYMLORP7L5WSJPJMWI.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FmlwkpbW-WK-o5xdbxiEO32-VAfM%3D%2F1325x745%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FOMBKHNPXXYMLORP7L5WSJPJMWI.gif&h=3eb6fbe5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】去年7月14日沙田遊行示威活動，演變成警民衝突，大批警員衝入新城市廣場驅散示威者。其間一名22歲青年被指用雨傘插警，遭控以襲警罪。案件經審訊後，裁判官李志豪指案中警員證供前後不一；即使案發過程千鈞一髮，在重要環節上亦不能出錯，惟警員解釋為何證供有矛盾的說法牽強，裁定青年罪名不成立，兼得訟費。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n聲言被傘尖觸碰屬「插中」<br />\n<br />\n李官昨裁決指，本案關鍵在於警署警長（俗稱士沙）陳明德（圖）作供的可信性。陳起初稱當日被雨傘插時已用手撥開，但後來庭上又稱被傘「插中」，說法有差異。李官明白事件千鈞一髮，但在重要環節上不能出錯。<br />\n<br />\n李官又指，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n辯方申請訟費，控方反對，指被告在現場行為可疑亦不合情理，並質疑被告「咁蹺」出現在警員追捕另一黑衣人的路線上。惟李官最終批准被告可獲逾三萬元訟費。<br />\n<br />\n被告早前供稱，當。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n案中警署警長作供時自言被。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：STCC181/20"},{"pid":"b8431eadd27d2d8caa29b43714b808cd754e3952","tid":2131697,"uid":277551,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T04:31:53.000Z","msg":"實情就係你講大話"},{"pid":"e09bfa8ff232716c2646bb8f4d9eaeddd65110f0","tid":2131697,"uid":127929,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T04:32:33.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\">警署警長陳明德</span>"},{"pid":"aecfed782c524bb7468e17261e3b345c449fce18","tid":2131697,"uid":47356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T04:35:20.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">警署警長陳明德</span></strong></span><br />\n仔女係邊"},{"pid":"cbd37d254c38555209ddfb94b836c01f213e5b3a","tid":2131697,"uid":122134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T04:35:23.000Z","msg":"咁講完大話<br />\n有無後果?<br />\n會唔會list做不可靠證人"},{"pid":"f44dcd44f1ef03046b2d5602472fd17114778da8","tid":2131697,"uid":59522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aecfed782c524bb7468e17261e3b345c449fce18","tid":2131697,"uid":47356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T04:35:20.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">警署警長陳明德</span></strong></span><br />\n仔女係邊"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T04:43:51.000Z","msg":"住邊？"}]}